-- Novartis Sales Force Covered by Federal Wage Laws, U.S. Appeals Court Says
-- Bob Van Voris
-- 2010-07-06T14:08:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/novartis-sales-force-covered-by-federal-wage-laws-u-s-appeals-court-says.html

          
          
             Novartis AG sales representatives are
covered by U.S. wage laws covering overtime pay, a federal
appeals court has ruled.  
